title: VanMoof

creator: VanMoof BV
descriptionHtml:
It’s all at your fingertips. Lock or unlock your bike, check the battery level, and find where you parked it – all from your phone. Keep an eye out for regular updates geared to take your VanMoof riding experience to the next level.

No matter where you are in the app, it will assist you with your smoothest ride yet:

Home
• No keys are needed, your bike smartly recognises you. Unlock your bike with just a tap or create a personal unlock code to easily unlock your bike without your phone.
• Check how much battery your bike has (and Powerbank if you have one).
• View your current speed, distance, and ride duration on your in-app live dashboard.
• Adjust your bike settings instantly on the home screen. You can change your motor assistance, gears, lights, bell sound, and other bike sounds.

Rides
• Look back at every trip with a detailed ride overview.
• You can view every journey, including the time, distance, maximum and average speed, if you stopped, and how much battery it cost.
• See how you compare to other VanMoof riders in your city and across the World.

Garage
• Find all of your bike information, change your bike settings, and view your My VanMoof profile.
• Get help with your bike by contacting support or reading the help articles.
• Share your bike with your friends and family.
• Plan a repair appointment at your closest store.
• Mark your bike as missing and send in the Bike Hunters.
• If your bike has Apple Find My, you can see the current status.

Supported bike models
• VanMoof S5 & A5
• VanMoof S3 & X3
• VanMoof S2 & X2
• VanMoof Electrified S & X
• VanMoof Smart S & X
• VanMoof Smartbike

Disclaimer: App features are dependent on your bike model.

Home
• No keys are needed, your bike smartly recognises you. Unlock your bike with just a tap or create a personal unlock code to easily unlock your bike without your phone.

Rides

• Mark your bike as missing and send in the Bike Hunters.
• If your bike has Apple Find My, you can see the current status.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We frequently have updates for your S5 & A5, so that’s why we wanted to make updating the bike easier for you. Starting with this release the app will automatically transfer the update to your bike whenever you’re nearby, and we’ll notify you when the update is ready to be installed. This means you can focus on other stuff while we’re doing updates in the background.

If you’re looking to spice up your homescreen you can now choose one of our colourful app icons!
